properties.Name: CustomerAccountProductServiceChannelFee
properties.Description:
A specific Schedule which is defined for or assigned to a Customer Account for an associated period.

Some accounts based on size or volume will have commission schedules defined just for them based on specific Products.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountId

Columns.Description: The minimum amount for which the associated Product Charge Schedule applies.

Columns.Name: MaximumAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum amount for which the associated Product Charge Schedule applies.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the product available channel relationship is valid.

Columns.Name: EffectiveStartDate
Columns.Description: The effective start date for which the associated Schedule is assigned to the Customer Account.

Columns.Name: EffectiveEndDate
Columns.Description: The effective end date for which the associated Schedule is assigned to the Customer Account.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountProductServiceChannelFeeAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the customer account product service channel fee.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountProductServiceChannelFeeNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Customer Account Product Service Channel Fee.
